dcterms:description: The TraumaBase R dataset is used to model the level of platelet upon arrival at the hospital from the clinical data of 15,785 patients, focusing on the impact of missing values in linear models.
dcterms:title: TraumaBase R

dcterms:description: The Superconductivity dataset contains 81 quantitative features from 21,263 superconductors, used to predict the critical temperature of each superconductor, introducing missing values to evaluate the proposed method.
dcterms:title: Superconductivity
